ZH: 我的运势今天非常好。
EN: My luck is very good today.

ZH: 他的运势一直都很不错。
EN: His luck has always been good.

ZH: 她的运势越来越好了。
EN: Her luck is getting better and better.

ZH: 这是一个非常不幸的运势。
EN: This is a very unlucky fortune.

ZH: 虽然他的运势不好，但他依然坚持下去。
EN: Although his luck is bad, he still perseveres.

ZH: 我希望运势能一直保持下去。
EN: I hope my luck will continue.

ZH: 他的运势突然变得非常糟糕。
EN: His luck suddenly became very bad.

ZH: 这个星期的运势对我来说是非常重要的。
EN: The fortune of this week is very important to me.

ZH: 她一直通过观察星座来了解自己的运势。
EN: She has always understood her fortune by observing constellations.

ZH: 那个顺利的项目将改变他的运势。
EN: That successful project will change his luck.

ZH: 运势是不能被预测的。
EN: Luck cannot be predicted.

ZH: 他的长辈告诉他相信运势。
EN: His elders told him to believe in fortune.

ZH: 这次的考试运势不容乐观。
EN: The fortune of this exam is not optimistic.

ZH: 我们不能完全依赖运势，还需要努力。
EN: We can't rely solely on fortune, we still need to work hard.

ZH: 她在网上查看了自己的运势。
EN: She checked her fortune online.

ZH: 我今天的运势很一般。
EN: My fortune today is average.

ZH: 这个婚礼会对他们的运势有所影响。
EN: This wedding will have an impact on their fortune.

ZH: 这个卦的运势是非常好的。
EN: The fortune of this divination is very good.

ZH: 他相信通过改变一些习惯，可以改变运势。
EN: He believes that by changing some habits, he can change his fortune.

ZH: 运势需要抓住机会时才会显现。
EN: Fortune only manifests when you seize the opportunity.
